      "lyrics": "Neon lights flash across the sky\nColors dancing, spirits high\nWe ride the wave of endless night\nSynthwave dreams ignite the light\n\nVerse 2:\nPixels glow beneath the moon\nElectric hearts play a cosmic tune\nLost in code and melody\nNeon lights set us free"
