      "genre": "Electronic",
      "isFavorite": true,
      "playCount": 28,
      "lyrics": "Waiting in a car, waiting for a ride in the dark\nThe city shimmers in the distance, cold\nDriving through the midnight streets\nSearching for the sound that never sleeps\n\nMidnight city, we never sleep\nRunning through the avenues so deep\nLights above, the stars align\nThis midnight city, forever mine"
    },
    {
